fields.label: Add CTA
fields.name: add_cta
fields.instructions: Adds a call to action to the bottom inside this layout

fields.label: CTA Content Background
fields.name: cta_content_background
fields.instructions: Include the gradient / solid color rounded background?

fields.label: Section ID
fields.name: section_id
fields.instructions: Only lowercase letters, numbers, hyphens, and underscores allowed. Cannot begin with a number.

sub_fields.label: Column Width
sub_fields.name: column_width
sub_fields.instructions: *Optional* Enter a percentage to set the width of this column. This will override the default width. If this is filled out, make sure all other columns width are set as well to keep the desired number of columns in a row.

sub_fields.label: Layout Height
sub_fields.name: layout_height
sub_fields.instructions: The layout height will either be controlled by the height of the visual or the content

sub_fields.label: Image Size
sub_fields.name: image_size
sub_fields.instructions: Contain will fit the image inside the container. Cover will stretch the image to the edge of container while maintaining aspect ratio

sub_fields.label: Posts Per Page
sub_fields.name: posts_per_page
sub_fields.instructions: Number of news posts listed before load more button

sub_fields.label: Message
sub_fields.message: Outputs a horizontal rule to divide setions.
